{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idd2130622-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4107"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4107"},"text":"§ 4107.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reports to Congress","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than six months after its organization, and every six months ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002122"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002122"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See Modification of Reporting Requirements note below."}],"tail":" thereafter, the Commission shall make a report to the Congress concerning its operations under this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idd2130623-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-07-03/ch826"},"text":"July 3, 1948, ch. 826","children":[],"tail":", title I, § 9, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/1246"},"text":"62 Stat. 1246","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/846/tI/s102"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–846, title I, § 102","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-22"},"text":"Oct. 22, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/76/1107"},"text":"76 Stat. 1107","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idd2130624-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"prospectiveAmendment","id":"idd2130625-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Annual Submission of Reports","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/348/s2/6"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–348, § 2(6)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-11-08"},"text":"Nov. 8, 1965","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/79/1312"},"text":"79 Stat. 1312","children":[],"tail":", modified the provisions of this section, beginning "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1967-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1967","children":[],"tail":", to require annual instead of semiannual submission to Congress by Foreign Claims Settlement Commission of report concerning its operations under War Claims Act of 1948."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idd2130626-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idd2130627-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subchapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this title”, meaning title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-07-03/ch826"},"text":"act July 3, 1948, ch. 826","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/1240"},"text":"62 Stat. 1240","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this subchapter. For complete classification of title I to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idd2130628-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to section 2008 of the former Appendix to this title prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idd2130629-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1962—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/846"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–846","children":[],"tail":" made technical amendment to reference in original act which appears in text as reference to this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idd213062a-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"idd213062b-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For provisions transferring Foreign Claims Settlement Commission of the United States to Department of Justice, as a separate agency, see section 1622a et seq. of Title 22, Foreign Relations and Intercourse.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idd213062c-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Modification of Reporting Requirements","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/348/s2/6"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–348, § 2(6)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-11-08"},"text":"Nov. 8, 1965","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/79/1312"},"text":"79 Stat. 1312","children":[],"tail":", modified the reporting requirements of this section as follows: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{},"text":"“Beginning ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1967-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1967","children":[],"tail":", from semiannual to annual submission to the Congress by the Foreign Claims Settlement Commission of the United States of a report concerning its operations under the War Claims Act of 1948 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/1246"},"text":"62 Stat. 1246","children":[],"tail":"; 50 U.S.C. App. 2008 [now "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4107"},"text":"50 U.S.C. 4107","children":[],"tail":"]).”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"idd213062d-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"idd213062e-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"War Claims Commission, including offices of its members, abolished and functions transferred to Foreign Claims Settlement Commission of the United States by Reorg. Plan No. 1 of 1954, §§ 2, 4, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1954-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1954","children":[],"tail":", 19 F.R. 3985, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68/1279"},"text":"68 Stat. 1279","children":[],"tail":", set out in the Appendix to Title 5, Government Organization and Employees. See, also, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4101"},"text":"section 4101 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and notes thereunder."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
